---
import Button from "./Button.astro";

const principles = [
  {
    label: "Resilience",
    body: "No single person or institution controls the DAO",
  },
  {
    label: "Inclusivity",
    body: "Scientists, engineers, students, and supporters all have a voice",
  },
  {
    label: "Scalability",
    body: "Governance evolves as the ecosystem grows",
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-plum-darkest text-cream py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8">
      Progressive decentralization
    </h2>
    <div
      class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 font-sans text-base text-cream/80 leading-relaxed"
    >
      <p>
        Though originally founded by three people, the Quantum Biology DAO was
        designed with progressive decentralization as an intentional goal.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over time, governance power will shift from the founding team to the
        broader community. This ensures:
      </p>
    </div>
    <ul class="max-w-3xl my-8 space-y-3 font-sans text-base text-cream/80">
      {
        principles.map((p) => (
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-cream/50">—</span>
            <span>
              <span class="font-bold text-cream">{p.label}:</span> {p.body}
            </span>
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>
    <p
      class="max-w-3xl font-sans text-base text-cream/80 leading-relaxed mb-10"
    >
      This is how we build toward a truly global, community-owned system for
      advancing open science.
    </p>
    <Button
      href="https://saurikz.com/what-is-progressive-decentralization-web3"
      variant="secondary"
      size="md"
      external>Read more about progressive decentralization</Button
    >
  </div>
</section>
